  "decision_conditions": [
    "Reason : 1 - This application cannot be considered under the prior approval process as the proposed works have commenced prior to the receipt by the developer from the local planning authority. Therefore, the proposal does not comply with Class A of Part 1 of Schedule 2 of the Town and Country Planning (General Permitted Development) (England) Order 2015.",
    "Reason : 2 - The rear extension, by reason of its scale, bulk, form, siting and massing, would be overbearing, unduly dominant and visually intrusive; resulting in an unacceptable loss of daylight, outlook and increased sense of enclosure toward the neighbouring properties 32 and 36 Aylward Road. The proposal would be contrary to policy CS 14 of the Merton LDF Core Planning Strategy (2011) and policies DM D2 and DM D3 of the Merton Sites and Policies Plan (2014)."
